  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nThe ``replica-healthcheck`` container is constantly crashing. Both ``data-transport-layer`` and ``l2geth-replica`` seem to be running. The only deviation from the documentation is I changed the ports in``replica-shared.yml`` from 8545, and 8546 to 8555 and 8556. Both ports are currently being used by Ethereum mainnet on the same host. A little help would be nice üôè\r\n\r\n```replica-healthcheck_1   | > @eth-optimism/replica-healthcheck@1.1.2 start\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   | > ts-node ./src/service\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   | \r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   | /opt/optimism/packages/common-ts/src/base-service/base-service-v2.ts:303\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   |         throw new Error(`missing required option: ${optionName}`)\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   |               ^\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   | Error: missing required option: referenceRpcProvider\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   |     at new BaseServiceV2 (/opt/optimism/packages/common-ts/src/base-service/base-service-v2.ts:303:15)\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   |     at new HealthcheckService (/opt/optimism/packages/replica-healthcheck/src/service.ts:34:5)\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   |     at Object.<anonymous> (/opt/optimism/packages/replica-healthcheck/src/service.ts:208:19)\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   |     at Module._compile (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1105:14)\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   |     at Module.m._compile (/opt/optimism/node_modules/ts-node/src/index.ts:1310:23)\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   |     at Module._extensions..js (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1159:10)\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   |     at Object.require.extensions.<computed> [as .ts] (/opt/optimism/node_modules/ts-node/src/index.ts:1313:12)\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   |     at Module.load (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:981:32)\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   |     at Function.Module._load (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:822:12)\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   |     at Function.executeUserEntryPoint [as runMain] (node:internal/modules/run_main:77:12)\r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   | npm ERR! Lifecycle script `start` failed with error: \r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   | npm ERR! Error: command failed \r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   | npm ERR!   in workspace: @eth-optimism/replica-healthcheck@1.1.2 \r\nreplica-healthcheck_1   | npm ERR!   at location: /opt/optimism/packages/replica-healthcheck \r\nop-replica_replica-healthcheck_1 exited with code 1```",
